{"tid":1004994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾半加人支持逮捕孟晚舟　44%主張對支那更強硬","createTime":"2019-02-02T01:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T04:17:22.000Z","uid":32511,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ea076344c5c72151bbe4e5a13c4e8fa3aa873030","tid":1004994,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T01:40:34.000Z","msg":"中國科技大廠華為財務長孟晚舟去年底遭加拿大逮捕後，引發中國一連串報復行動。最新民調顯示，逾5成加拿大人認為加拿大應美國引渡要求逮捕孟晚舟是對的。另有逾4成受訪者則認為加國政府應該對中國更加強硬。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音報導，加拿大民調機構安格斯里德策略研究機構（Angus Reid Institute）昨日公布最新民調，55%受訪者認為逮捕孟晚舟是正確決定；92%受訪者認為目前加拿大和中國的緊張關係「相當嚴重」，或「很嚴重」；有52%的人對加拿大總理杜魯多處理加中兩國關係感到不滿；44%的人說，他們希望杜魯多對中國更加強硬。<br />\n<br />\n中國在孟晚舟被逮捕之後，將加拿大公民康明凱(Michael Kovrig)和在中國經營企業的史派佛（Michael Spavor）以「危害國家安全」為由拘捕，並在謝倫伯格(Robert LloydSchellenberg)被控販毒一案中將他改判死刑。中國的這一系列所作所為被認為是對加拿大逮捕孟晚舟的報復，是北京當局正在與加拿大進行的一場人質外交。<br />\n<br />\n大部分受訪加拿大人都認為，在人權問題上，中國是「不可信的」，很多人認為人權和法治應該是加中兩國關係中最重要的一個方面。近2/3 (62%) 的人說，在兩國關係中，中國的人權紀錄和法治應該比貿易和投資機會更加重要。"},{"pid":"e80aeb9df97c835fbaf01e137daa30089739b5b4","tid":1004994,"uid":57376,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:19:30.000Z","msg":"加拿大華人集體沉默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace526b5ead836ab795cf2eaa9c0c4bd744d0ae0","tid":1004994,"uid":63154,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e80aeb9df97c835fbaf01e137daa30089739b5b4","tid":1004994,"uid":57376,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:19:30.000Z","msg":"加拿大華人集體沉默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:22:22.000Z","msg":"真正嘅華人：關我叉事，識佢條毛咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只有中共外圍組織先出黎嘈"},{"pid":"057f1e6ad09333d690c7db98eabfbd64bce2cd79","tid":1004994,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ace526b5ead836ab795cf2eaa9c0c4bd744d0ae0","tid":1004994,"uid":63154,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e80aeb9df97c835fbaf01e137daa30089739b5b4","tid":1004994,"uid":57376,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:19:30.000Z","msg":"加拿大華人集體沉默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:22:22.000Z","msg":"真正嘅華人：關我叉事，識佢條毛咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只有中共外圍組織先出黎嘈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:24:25.000Z","msg":"我唔想返支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc371e304155d4f07dd4a71d1a5ddeba063fdf8","tid":1004994,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:29:54.000Z","msg":"三戰不是夢<br />\n<br />\n樓價跌跌跌 銀紙當廁紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b7620b04a4f8a4a538956e7c44362699dd649c","tid":1004994,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:16:38.000Z","msg":"連加拿大呢d偏向liberal既國家都比支那推成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca19ebfbfe78221164e4091bb8840d2dd912251","tid":1004994,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01b7620b04a4f8a4a538956e7c44362699dd649c","tid":1004994,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:16:38.000Z","msg":"連加拿大呢d偏向liberal既國家都比支那推成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:14:17.000Z","msg":"支那獨力改變大愛左膠加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n彰顯支國實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58813dd252c1a08272a2bb4a58f0e090170eed57","tid":1004994,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:17:22.000Z","msg":"加拿大同冰島一樣，自然資源足，唔同人做生意都不會餓死，選了條廢物做總理"}]}